reviews.text: Authentic 四川菜 in very good quality and friendly staff. Prices are affordable. Place is small, better book a table.
Staff are very helpful, food are quite traditionally Sichuan style and spice/hotness can be adjusted. Zhangxiang Duck and Ganguo Pig's offal.

Sichuan style spicy food. Signature dish is cold pot fish, very spicy, the sauce is a bit like chili curry; chicken pot is good too. Good service.
